text:
Nose: strong bananas and yeast;
Appearance: Head is extremely carbonated, the head has such fine white bubbles as to be creamy and pours three fingers easily; body is golden straw color.  
Mouthfeel:  creamy, rich texture.  
Taste:  Spices, coriander, cloves; surprisingly little bananas; 
Overall:  Not as good as Aventinus or Weihenstephaner weizenbocks.  Enjoyable but not worth the price.
